<i>Gatinho feliz,
Gatinho dorminhoco</i>

238
00:11:17,908 --> 00:11:20,935
<i>Miau, miau, miau</i>

239
00:11:20,945 --> 00:11:23,823
<i>Mentiroso macio,
Mentiroso quentinho</i>

240
00:11:23,833 --> 00:11:26,873
<i>Bolinha de trapaça</i>

241
00:11:26,883 --> 00:11:29,977
<i>Mentiroso feliz,
Mentiroso dorminhoco</i>

242
00:11:29,987 --> 00:11:33,156
<i>Trapaça, trapaça, trapaça</i>

243
